<mxCell id="n9" value="Five CI principles (ContinuousIntegration p.3):&#10;1. Environments based on stability&#10;2. Maintain a code repository&#10;3. Commit frequently and build every commit&#10;4. Make the build self-testing&#10;5. Keep the build fast&#10;&#10;Lab pipeline runs all phases in one command:&#10;mvn --batch-mode clean verify (CILab p.1)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=8;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="40" y="400" width="420" height="190" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
